    <ul>
      <h2>Mockup Ideas</h2>
      <h3>You can create concept mockups like:</h3>
      <li>
        The Painters Portfolio A homepage that mimics a physical sketchbook or
        gallery wall. Scrolling feels like flipping pages.
      </li>
      <li>
        The Storytellers Scroll A long-form landing page styled like a
        storybook—each section is a “chapter” in the brand’s journey.
      </li>
      <li>
        The Makers Bench A grid-style site that looks like a workspace, with
        tool icons, sticky notes, and pinned inspirations alongside project
        work.
      </li>
    </ul>

